  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0baf\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4 \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4 \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Passenger train services will come to a complete standstill if fuel is not supplied - Rail Services Union",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The passenger train service will come to a complete standstill in the coming days if the Ministry of Power does not take appropriate steps to distribute the necessary fuel to rehabilitate the railway workers.",
        "The railway service unions point out that the railway service alone is the ultimate solution for the general public in the transport media.",
        "Fuel shortages have had a massive impact on public transportation. Public and private buses are limited in service due to fuel shortages.",
        "Due to the sharp increase in bus fares, the public has started using the train service more and more instead of using the bus service.",
        "However, congestion on buses is high. In some areas it was observed that the public was traveling unsafely sitting on the roof of the bus.",
        "The Department of Railways said last week that there were no problems with the supply of fuel for the train service.",
        "There is a huge difference between the number of passengers using the train service and the number of trains involved in the service.",
        "The Department of Railways has stated that it is not possible to increase the number of public service trains.",
        "Yesterday 28 train services and today 22 train services were canceled due to fuel shortage which has had an impact on the service delivery of train servicemen. As well as train services were delayed.",
        "Unrest was seen at Fort Railway Station as 22 train services were canceled today due to non-socialization of train staff.",
        "The public commuters who had been waiting for a long time for the train service have protested because of the cancellation of the train service.",
        "The government has not provided the necessary facilities to continue the railway service as it has been declared as an essential service through the Gazette notification.",
        "The government has repeatedly ignored the need to prioritize rail service over fuel supply.",
        "Due to the shortage of fuel and the increase in bus fares, the general public is now increasingly using the train service. Rail service is currently the only final solution in public transport.",
        "Officials in charge of the railway station said that if no proper action is taken to distribute fuel to the railway workers, the train service will be completely stopped in the coming days."
      ],
